reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great customer support
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these headphones for my daughter in June 2023. Recently, both sides stopped working (I didn't know, but a few weeks ago, one side had stopped working). It's been months, but I figured I'd try emailing their customer support. I got an immediate response asking for my order number. They said that they didn't have the same color anymore, but if I could pick another color, they'd ship a new one out to me. I've had bad experiences where I never received the item after these assurances, but sure enough, a couple days later, a new pair of headphones arrived. They worked perfectly and my daughter is very happy.On top of their great customer support, these are just a nice pair of headphones that fold up neatly for travel and look good. My daughter has a few other pairs of headphones collected over the years but these remain her go-to. She says that they're "comfortable and pretty".

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my child who loves them! They look good and sound great! They fit real comfortably, and my child said the headphones helped him to hear things in his online game that he couldn't hear before. Well worth the money. Would buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works good but had some issues Due to user error
reviews.reviewText: Great product honestly loved them to the point where I would literally keep buying them even though they stopped working after a couple of months longest I've been able to keep a pair is about six months the shortest time was maybe about two months before it just stops working or one of the sides goes out or the cord starts acting up and cuts in and out the mic quality was excellent never had an issue with that at all very clear used it all the time as I was doing things and was on the phone talking to a friend or even a work call great sound quality it's just like I said most of the time the cord would go out and so the music would start cutting in and out but that honestly could have been due to my own personal errors and using them for everything including working out and so it could just have been abuse on my end

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are really nice for the price. They block out sound and the volume is good. Doesn't need a volume button on the earphones themselves. Just use your phone volume, obviously! These are great! Nice color, too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Take a lot of adjusting! Tight for a while.
reviews.reviewText: Bought these to replace the headset I currently have, and still use. Too busy to return so mostly use them when watching shows on my tablet. They started very tight around my head, and crushed my ears, I had to really adjust them to get them to fit right.The sound is alright, and there's no noise cancelling, I can hear everything around me, and the volume on these isn't the greatest. The folding hinges were so tight that even with the height adjustment; they wanted to stay folded. I ended up sticking them around a pillow for a couple of weeks, forgot about them, and then found them to be pretty reasonable to wear now.Definitely thinking of using them with my VR headset later as the other headphones I have don't fit around it. Will update if it goes as planned, or if they just become a conveniently matching pair to use with my tablet.
